channel.title: Ajscape updates(list)
channel.description:
AJScape v5 SERVER
~Updates~ Added winter pkbox!!! Fixed Ice Barrage Added Range Guild Added Working Flax and Bowstring Added Full Guthan Effects Wildy is only pking area Added Working Ring of Stone Max Stat 99 Added Agility 99% real rs max hit Removed Password Encryption Added Handy Pocket Portals Added Torso Mini-Game Added a easy way to runecraft Restore Prayer with altar Reveals those who try using p ring When u die u go to hell Added thieving stalls Added Mining Fixed Disconnect when u die error Unlimited Energy Split Private Chat Saves Added Altar and Range target(Gives xp and rune arrows) Wearing A Scythe Makes You The Grim Reaper New client to download for better play Added Update timer Telegrab Fixed Custom Character menu Added Herblore Added Dragon Smithing Added Cooking Fixed Training Error Added Proper Clan System Added ultimate spell
~Updates list 2~ Made Training faster on hay,door,dummy Removed the skull that said 690008 All partyhats are untradeable Fixing the dieing when you're below 50HP & Get barraged error
Added Defenders(Daggers) Added Pk Portal for 377 cache clients Healing spell(you)- Lvl 40 Normal spell Got rid of nulls
~Newest Updates~ Winter pkbox added thanks to ideas Added Portal Room Added Full Construction Fixed Ranging Speed fixed NPC training Fixed wep delays took out the noob spammers, aka knights took out the bank thing, made only 1 jad... fixed item prices + bonouses cleaned client.java more space took out the econmy ruiner commands autolog out reduced client.java to 993 kb. took out the bank think in emote tabs Runecrafting woo NO MORE OBJECT TRAINING
